{"TopicId":118248,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"KSP Mega-Truck 2.0 (Halloween Edition)","CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T00:20:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T00:20:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EIntroducing The apocalypse KSP Mega-Truck 2.0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Qmz3ZDs.png\u0022 alt=\u0022Qmz3ZDs.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EThe ultimate vehicle for all your apocalyptic needs.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/aZIM6ElIc5c?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EDirections:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDecouple the axles from the chassis of the vehicle by pressing the space-bar. Using the trim commands [Holding Alt\u002BE] to have the axles automatically turn on electric power. Make sure their SAS is not activated to keep it from stopping the rotation. Then switch back to the main vessel and use the jets as your primary source of power. Turn using the Q and E keys or press \u0022Control here\u0022 from the underneath probe core and steer using A and D.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#B22222;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload it here:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/x6hwm80qpqhqamo/MEGA%20TRUCK%202_0%20%28Apocalypse%29.craft?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/x6hwm80qpqhqamo/MEGA%20TRUCK%202_0%20%28Apocalypse%29.craft?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Original Mega-Truck: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/109311-Jon-s-Mega-Truck-Mountain-Climber\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/109311-Jon-s-Mega-Truck-Mountain-Climber\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-11-01T01:57:41Z\u0022 title=\u002211/01/2015 01:57  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 1, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Jon144\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T00:24:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs it even near a fairing or cargo bay? That\u0027s probably your problem, things even slightly clipping with a fairing or cargo bay will quickly explode. It\u0027s a well-know bug, it destroyed my orion and constellation landers aeroshells.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lego8_bit","CreatedById":58076,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T03:05:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHave you Tried the alt f-12 method and allow clipping for that to work?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacetraindriver","CreatedById":149403,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T03:17:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat does it say on f3?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Majorjim!","CreatedById":61954,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T14:10:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESquad know their heating system is broken. Hopefully they will fix it soon. Until then you just have to find what part is causing it and work around it. You may need to rebuild the craft but it is fixable. I have had to rebuild my current WIP mission pack three times now. Annoying as it is, I am now super fast at it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T18:44:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for all your help! I fixed it and it works great now.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-12T20:02:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jon144\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Jon144\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThanks for all your help! I fixed it and it works great now.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027re welcome! Can\u0027t wait to see it action.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-13T02:49:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you didn\u0027t notice I added a video of it working. And now edited the entire post. Download is now available.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-08-13T03:04:38Z\u0022 title=\u002208/13/2015 03:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 13, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Jon144\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-17T04:24:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPrepare for a Halloween pumpkin-spiced flavored upgrade.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-17T17:42:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDon\u0027t keep us waiting too long :-)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jon144","CreatedById":80626,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-01T01:58:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHappy Halloween!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-03T17:09:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAh, finally!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}